{"tid":1785162,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【媒體姓黨】新修訂新聞工作者準則 強調用習思想武裝頭腦正面宣傳","createTime":"2019-12-16T07:35:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T10:57:23.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d50e5c1491437fbce783486f9275d3f5bdc9adba","tid":1785162,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T07:35:21.000Z","msg":"內地今年才透過「學習強國」手機App內容考試，完成換發全國新聞編採人員的記者證，現又在相隔10年後，再次修訂《中國新聞工作者職業道德準則》，這份準則開宗明義就強調中國新聞事業的政治性，其中提出新聞工作者要堅持用「習近平新時代中國特色社會主義思想」武裝頭腦，堅持新聞真實性原則，着重講好中國故事；強調正面宣傳及「堅持正確輿論導向」。<br />\n<br />\n新修訂的《中國新聞工作者職業道德準則》15日公佈，準則內容除了對新聞工作的一般要求，包括堅持新聞真實性原則、努力到現場採訪核實、遵守法律和尊重版權等新聞規範外，也包含了許多中國特色。準則強調「堅持正確輿論導向。堅持團結穩定鼓勁、正面宣傳為主，弘揚主旋律、傳播正能量，不斷鞏固和壯大積極健康向上的主流思想輿論」；在遵守法律紀律方面，準則指出要切實維護國家政治安全、文化安全和社會穩定。<br />\n<br />\n作為中共的宣傳機器，這份準則稱，中國的新聞工作對外要展示良好形象，「講好中國的故事、中國共產黨的故事、中國特色社會主義的故事、中國人民的故事，讓世界更好地讀懂中國」。同時因應網絡發展，這份準則表示要強化網絡思維，深刻把握傳統媒體和新興媒體融合發展的趨勢，也要適應分眾化、差異化傳播趨勢，「主動設置議題，善於因勢利導」，不斷提高影響力。<br />\n這是自1991年準則頒佈以來第4次修訂，上次修訂時間為2009年11月。中共近年多次強化對新聞工作的控管，今年9月中共中宣部規定，全國新聞編採人員必須在「學習強國」手機App上，通過「習思想」等相關內容的考試才能申領新版記者證。<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191216/large/1576473401_1ac6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191216%2Flarge%2F1576473401_1ac6.jpg&h=fa4ae3cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191216/60382982\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191216%2F60382982&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7hR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=d71da9ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191216%2F60382982&h=bf17496e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191216/60382982</a>"},{"pid":"f65a424c9b7ae26b03bd2eef7272425f54ad173c","tid":1785162,"uid":112709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T07:41:08.000Z","msg":"共匪真係下下都柒撚到喊"},{"pid":"6ea3a20e6870525809ddbc618f57e420a2c2f314","tid":1785162,"uid":324602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T07:43:34.000Z","msg":"洗腦咪洗腦 係要搞d術語出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3256484b9cd46c7eac20c2da208c101e76b72ea","tid":1785162,"uid":61197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T08:15:34.000Z","msg":"呢篇新聞反映中国人每日接觸嘅媒體全部有立場同親政府,好易比人煽動<br />\n<br />\n所以有時同佢地討論唔需要太認真, 全部都比人洗哂腦"},{"pid":"7cb77a5a7dd8f14716197cf83c31776ab3053a38","tid":1785162,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T08:17:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZZ5SvmN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZZ5SvmN.jpg&h=94ed4d4b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PooHSz8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPooHSz8.jpg&h=0cfd4735&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qc9Pxz9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQc9Pxz9.jpg&h=b72c3d63&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6DCUJGQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6DCUJGQ.jpg&h=9f6d5e7e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"993bd818aec7fb07412cc725f2b4a965d1b3a003","tid":1785162,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T08:45:46.000Z","msg":"CLS <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bedf42fe16704aea78e936580856c8e66d48c072","tid":1785162,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T08:48:03.000Z","msg":"不如直接命令記者唔好採訪用新聞聯播份稿<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b62c2b54081952314840bd5eede4b8de1b11b0f4","tid":1785162,"uid":